        </Str>
        <Disp Icon="Str" />
      </Item>
      <Item ItemId=";SHARPIE0009" ItemType="0;.resx" PsrId="211" Leaf="true">
        <Str Cat="Text">
          <Val><![CDATA[Failed to the SDK path ('xcrun --show-sdk-path' failed): {0}]]></Val>
          <Tgt Cat="Text" Stat="Loc" Orig="New">
            <Val><![CDATA[SDK 경로('xcrun --show-sdk-path' 실패) 실패: {0}]]></Val>
          </Tgt>
        </Str>
        <Disp Icon="Str" />
      </Item>
      <Item ItemId=";SHARPIE0010" ItemType="0;.resx" PsrId="211" Leaf="true">
        <Str Cat="Text">
          <Val><![CDATA[The path to clang's resource directory is required.]]></Val>
          <Tgt Cat="Text" Stat="Loc" Orig="New">
            <Val><![CDATA[clang의 리소스 디렉터리에 대한 경로가 필요합니다.]]></Val>
          </Tgt>
        </Str>
        <Disp Icon="Str" />
      </Item>
      <Item ItemId=";SHARPIE0011" ItemType="0;.resx" PsrId="211" Leaf="true">
        <Str Cat="Text">
          <Val><![CDATA[The specified clang resource directory does not exist: {0}]]></Val>
          <Tgt Cat="Text" Stat="Loc" Orig="New">
            <Val><![CDATA[지정한 clang 리소스 디렉터리 없음: {0}]]></Val>
          </Tgt>
        </Str>
        <Disp Icon="Str" />
      </Item>
      <Item ItemId=";SHARPIE0012" ItemType="0;.resx" PsrId="211" Leaf="true">
        <Str Cat="Text">
          <Val><![CDATA[Could not find the clang resource directory, because it doesn't look like we're executing from inside a NuGet.]]></Val>
          <Tgt Cat="Text" Stat="Loc" Orig="New">
            <Val><![CDATA[NuGet 내부에서 실행 중이 아닌 것 같아 clang 리소스 디렉터리를 찾을 수 없습니다.]]></Val>
          </Tgt>
        </Str>
        <Disp Icon="Str" />
      </Item>
      <Item ItemId=";SHARPIE0013" ItemType="0;.resx" PsrId="211" Leaf="true">
        <Str Cat="Text">
          <Val><![CDATA[Could not find the clang resource directory, because the directory {0} doesn't exist.]]></Val>
          <Tgt Cat="Text" Stat="Loc" Orig="New">
            <Val><![CDATA[디렉터리 {0}이(가) 없어서 clang 리소스 디렉터리를 찾을 수 없습니다.]]></Val>
          </Tgt>
        </Str>
        <Disp Icon="Str" />
      </Item>
      <Item ItemId=";SHARPIE0014" ItemType="0;.resx" PsrId="211" Leaf="true">
        <Str Cat="Text">
          <Val><![CDATA[The framework '{0}' was specified in the excluded frameworks list but was not found in the SDK.]]></Val>
          <Tgt Cat="Text" Stat="Loc" Orig="New">
            <Val><![CDATA[프레임워크 '{0}'이(가) 제외된 프레임워크 목록에 지정되었지만 SDK에서 찾을 수 없습니다.]]></Val>
          </Tgt>
